name: Garlic Honey Chicken Breast
description: Pan-seared chicken breast with garlic and honey, golden on the outside and juicy inside, lightly sweet with a hint of garlic.

name: Honey Teriyaki Chicken Breast
description: Pan-seared chicken breast with a honey-soy glaze, crispy outside, tender inside, a perfect healthy and flavorful option.

name: Curry Lemon Chicken Breast
description: Pan-seared chicken breast with a blend of curry and lemon, fragrant and tangy, offering a burst of fresh flavor.

name: Korean Spicy Chicken Breast
description: Pan-seared chicken breast with Korean spicy sauce, blending sweetness and heat for a tender and flavorful dish.

name: Miso Glazed Chicken Breast
description: Chicken breaast marinated in miso paste and seared to perfection, offering a rich, savory flavor.

name: New Orleans Spiced Chicken
description: Pan-seared chicken breast with New Orleans spices, crispy on the outside, tender inside, with a balanced spicy flavor.

name: Soy Braised Beef Shank
description: Selected beef shank is slowly braised with soy sauce, oyster sauce, and a variety of spices. The meat is tender with a rich, flavorful sauce.

name: Spiced Braised Chicken Leg
description: Chicken leg braised with star anise, cinnamon, and other aromatic spices. Tender and juicy, this dish is a low-fat, high-protein choice, perfect for fitness enthusiasts.

name: Pickled Veg Chicken Stir-fry
description: Crisp pickled vegetables and tender bamboo shoots stir-fried with lean chicken breast, creating a refreshing, light, and nutritious dish.

name: Cilantro Chicken with Vinegar
description: Chicken breast mixed with cilantro, vinegar, chili, soy sauce, and oyster sauce. This tangy, refreshing dish is high in protein, perfect for fitness diets and light daily meals.

name: Chicken-Stuffed Bean Curd Rolls
description: Minced chicken wrapped in soft bean curd sheets, steamed with ginger and seasonings. Tender, juicy, and packed with flavor, this is a healthy, light meal option.

name: Steamed Egg with Chicken
description: Smooth steamed egg paired with savory minced chicken, seasoned with ginger and rice wine. A high-protein, low-fat, and nutritious dish.

name: Wine-Marinated Pig Tongue
description: Pig tongue marinated in traditional wine sauce, tender and flavorful with a rich, aromatic taste.

name: Wine-Marinated Chicken Gizzards
description: Crisp and tender chicken gizzards marinated in wine sauce, full of flavor. Perfect as a snack or appetizer.

name: Wine-Marinated Chicken Hearts
description: Tender chicken hearts marinated in wine sauce, offering a rich and unique flavor, perfect as a nutritious snack.
